frozen.name: glibc-mtrace
frozen.shortDescription: Perl script used to interpret and provide human readable output of the trace log contained in the file mtracedata, whose contents were produced by mtrace(3).
frozen.longDescription:
Any Unix-like operating system needs a C library: the library which
        defines the "system calls" and other basic facilities such as
        open, malloc, printf, exit...

        The GNU C library is used as the C library in the GNU system and
        most systems with the Linux kernel.
